Package dimstyl.orm.exceptions

package dimstyl.orm.exceptions
Contains exception classes related to ORM operations.
  • Exception Classes
    Class
    Description
    CompositePrimaryKeyException
    Exception thrown when a composite primary key is detected in an entity.
    DatabaseConnectionException
    Exception thrown when a database connection issue occurs.
    InvalidColumnNameException
    Exception thrown when an invalid column name is detected.
    MissingColumnAnnotationException
    Exception thrown when a required @Column annotation is missing from an entity field.
    MissingDatabaseAnnotationException
    Exception thrown when an entity class is missing the required @Database annotation.
    MissingPrimaryKeyException
    Exception thrown when an entity class does not have a primary key defined.
    MissingRepositoryAnnotationException
    Exception thrown when a repository class is missing the required @Repository annotation.
    MissingTableAnnotationException
    Exception thrown when an entity class is missing the required @Table annotation.
    SqlExecutionException
    Exception thrown when an error occurs during SQL execution.
    UnsupportedFieldTypeException
    Exception thrown when an unsupported field type is encountered in an entity.
